<task id="task_6C24E4C7932342D1A6B090A679A9FE95">
  <title>Compare Target Data with Analytics Package Data</title>
  <shortdesc>It's important to compare Target and analytical package data early
	 in your integration. Understand differences before launching your campaign or
	 test. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody>
    <steps id="steps_78B43762C08542C9A6B4B4AEFEC9C067">
      <step id="step_0D8811C2979D4F9F9F1B407B053E4A31">
        <cmd>Set up a simple 
			 <xref href="t_Creating_a_Monitoring_Campaign.xml#task_833A68CC388044FFA3AA3FED3276389D" type="task" format="dita" scope="local">Monitoring Campaign</xref> with a
			 single display mbox, the conversion mbox and at least one 
			 <xref href="c_Managing_Success_Metrics.xml#concept_F2D06B8EDCC24EED9C494210C1415859" type="concept" format="dita" scope="local">success metric</xref> in between. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
      <step id="step_8DFBCD655AA544E6A1AB91498FE42014">
        <cmd>Serve 
			 <xref href="c_About_Mboxes.xml#concept_E01933A6CEDE481BBAC25F95FE3C6FD9" type="concept" format="dita" scope="local">default content</xref> so there is
			 no change to the visitor's experience of your Web site. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
      <step id="step_4DC39A6E3AC64518A91F151FEC393E1D">
        <cmd>Approve the campaign and run it for a few days. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
      <step id="step_BF045FF3FD5A4E1180AD699A87B14F96">
        <cmd>When ready, compare Target reports data and your analytical
			 package data. 
		  </cmd>
        <stepresult>
          <p>Any differences should be due to the differences listed above. If
				there is an inexplicable mismatch, ask your representative to do further tests
				to gather more information about the visitors. 
			 </p>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
